forge.menu.updatescreen.title: Mod Update
forge.configgui.removeErroringEntities.t: Set 'tis t' true t' remove any Entity that be throwin' an error in its update method instead o' closin' th' server an' reportin' a crash log. BE WARNED 'TIS COULD SCREW UP EVERYTHIN' USE SPARIN'LY WE NAH BE RESPONSIBLE FER DAMAGES.
forge.configgui.removeErroringBlockEntit: Set 'tis t' true t' remove any BlockEntity that be throwin' an error in its update method instead o' closin' th' server an' reportin' a crash log. BE WARNED 'TIS COULD SCREW UP EVERYTHIN' USE SPARIN'LY WE NAH BE RESPONSIBLE FER DAMAGES.
forge.configgui.fullBoundingBoxLadders.t: Set 'tis t' true t' check th' entire entity's collision boundin' box fer ladders instead o' just th' block they be in. Causes noticeable differences in mechanics so default be vanilla behavior. Default: false.
forge.configgui.zombieBaseSummonChance.t: Base zombie summonin' spawn chance. Allows changin' th' bonus zombie summonin' mechanic.
forge.configgui.zombieBabyChance.tooltip: Chance that a zombie (or subclass) be a baby. Allows changin' th' zombie spawnin' mechanic.
forge.configgui.logCascadingWorldGenerat: Log cascadin' chunk generation issues durin' terrain population.
forge.configgui.fixVanillaCascading.tool: Fix vanilla issues that be causin' worldgen cascadin'. 'Tis DOES change vanilla worldgen so DO NAH report bugs related t' world differences if 'tis flag be on.
forge.configgui.dimensionUnloadQueueDela: Th' time in ticks th' server will wait when a dimension be queued t' unload. 'Tis can be useful when rapidly loadin' an' unloadin' dimensions, like e.g. throwin' loot through a nether portal a few time per second.
forge.configgui.clumpingThreshold.toolti: Controls th' number threshold at which Packet51 be preferred over Packet52, default an' minimum 64, maximum 1024.
forge.configgui.treatEmptyTagsAsAir.tool: Vanilla will be treatin' craftin' recipes usin' empty tags as air, an' allow ye t' craft wit' nothin' in that slot. 'Tis changes empty tags t' use BARRIER as th' item. T' prevent craftin' wit' air.
Skip checkin' if an ingredient be empty durin' shapeless recipe deserialization t' prevent complex ingredients from cachin' tags too early.
forge.configgui.skipEmptyShapelessCheck: Skip checkin' fer empty ingredients in Shapeless Recipe Deserialization
forge.configgui.forceSystemNanoTime.tool: Force th' use o' System.nanoTime instead o' glfwGetTime as th' main client Time provider.
forge.configgui.zoomInMissingModelTextIn: Toggle off t' make missin' model text in th' gui fit inside th' slot.
Zoom in Missin' model text in th' GUI
forge.configgui.forgeCloudsEnabled.toolt: Enable uploadin' cloud geometry t' th' GPU fer faster renderin'.
Disable cullin' o' hidden faces next t' stairs an' slabs. Causes extra renderin', but may fix some resource packs that be exploiting 'tis vanilla mechanic.
forge.configgui.alwaysSetupTerrainOffThr:
Enable Forge t' queue all chunk updates t' th' Chunk Update thread.
May increase FPS significantly, but may be also causin' weird renderin' lag.
Nah recommended fer computers wit'out a significant number o' cores available.
forge.configgui.forgeLightPipelineEnable: Enable th' Forge block renderin' pipeline - fixes th' lightin' o' custom models.
forge.configgui.selectiveResourceReloadE: When enabled, makes specific reload tasks such as lingo changin' quicker t' run.
forge.configgui.showLoadWarnings.tooltip: When enabled, Forge be showin' any warnin's that occurred durin' loadin'.
forge.configgui.disableVersionCheck.tool: Set t' true t' disable Forge version check mechanics. Forge be wantin' a small json file on our server fer version information. Fer more details see th' ForgeVersion class in our github.
forge.configgui.cachePackAccess.tooltip: Set 'tis t' true t' cache resource listin's in resource an' data packs
forge.configgui.indexVanillaPackCachesOn: Set 'tis t' true t' index vanilla resource an' data packs on thread
Index vanilla resource packs on thread
forge.configgui.indexModPackCachesOnThre: Set 'tis t' true t' index mod resource an' data packs on thread
Index mod resource packs on thread
forge.configgui.stabilizeDirectionGetNea: When enabled, a slightly biased Direction#getNearest calculation will be used to prevent normal fighting on 45 degree angle faces.
forge.configgui.calculateAllNormals.tool: During block model baking, manually calculates the normal for all faces. You will need to reload your resources to see results.
